# Test Cases

| TC ID | Scenario | Preconditions | Steps | Expected Result | Priority |
|-------|----------|--------------|-------|----------------|----------|
| TC-01 | Successful user registration | User not logged in | Enter valid data → Submit | Account created & confirmation shown | High |
| TC-02 | Registration with existing email | Email already registered | Enter existing email → Submit | Proper error message displayed | High |
| TC-03 | Successful login | Valid user exists | Enter valid credentials → Login | Redirect to dashboard | High |
| TC-04 | Login with incorrect password | Valid user exists | Enter wrong password → Login | Error message shown | High |
| TC-05 | Session expiration after logout | User logged in | Logout → Navigate back | User cannot access protected page | High |
| TC-06 | Add multiple products to cart | Product list available | Add 2 products | Cart updates correctly | High |
| TC-07 | Cart total price calculation | Product in cart | Change quantity | Total recalculates correctly | High |
| TC-08 | Negative quantity input | Product in cart | Enter -1 | System prevents invalid input | Medium |
| TC-09 | Successful checkout | Product in cart | Complete form with valid data | Order confirmation displayed | High |
| TC-10 | Checkout with missing required fields | On checkout page | Leave mandatory fields empty | Inline validation messages shown | High |
| TC-11 | Search with valid keyword | Home page | Enter product name | Relevant results displayed | Medium |
| TC-12 | Search with no results | Home page | Enter random string | “No results” message displayed | Low |
